, sans-serif;\">自助餐</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">异域料理</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">茶饮烘焙</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">快餐小吃</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 65.0pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" rowspan=\"6\" width=\"87\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">休闲娱乐</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom