5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">剧本杀</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">按摩SPA/洗浴</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 65.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"87\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">丽人/养生</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">SPA</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">按摩</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">美甲美睫</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">美发</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 65.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"87\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">生活服务</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">摄影写真</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 13.2pt;\"><td style=\"width: 154.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 13.2pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"205\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">婚庆服务</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、京东到店券过期退随时退服务规则说明</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、随时退</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">定义：消费者购买的京东到店券购买成功且未消费，消费者可以随时申请退券退款；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">退款时效：自消费者申请退款之日起1~7个工作日，券对应订单实付金额将原路退至消费者付款的账户。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">退款说明：</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在退款时，京东平台将扣除消费者购买该券时通过评价或晒单所获得的京豆及相应优惠，如消费者账户京豆已使用，则从退款金额中相应扣除。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、过期退</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">定义：消费者成功购买的京东到店券过期且未消费，京东平台将自动发起退券退款；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">退款时效：自京东平台发起退款日起，1~7个工作日，券对应订单实付金额将原路退至消费者付款的账户；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">退款说明：</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在退款时，京东平台将扣除购买该券时通过评价或晒单所获得的京豆及相应优惠，如消费者账户京豆已使用，则从退款金额中相应扣除。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、以上退款服务仅适用于商品页面注明支持&ldquo;随时退&rdquo;和/或&ldquo;过期退&rdquo;的商品和服务。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本次调整于2022年12月20日公示，将于2022年12月30日正式生效。对于上述售后服务体验提升公告如有其他疑问，请您拨打商家客服热线400-622-9068，或可以通过商家后台主界面右侧悬浮&ldquo;京灵智能助手&rdquo;联系商家在线客服。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">感谢您的支持与配合！&nbsp; </span></p>",
